led SR, Supe SS, Sathiyan S. Dosimetric comparison of high dose rate brachytherapy and intensity-modulated radiation therapy for cervical carcinoma. <em>J Med Phys</em> 2011;36(2):111–116.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.4103/0971-6203.79687">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21731228/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Dosimetric+comparison+of+high+dose+rate+brachytherapy+and+intensity-modulated+radiation+therapy+for+cervical+carcinoma&amp;author=B+Shwetha&amp;author=M+Ravikumar&amp;author=SR+Palled&amp;author=SS+Supe&amp;author=S+Sathiyan&amp;publication_year=2011&amp;journal=J+Med+Phys&amp;pages=111-116&amp;doi=10.4103%2F0971-6203.79687&amp;pmid=21731228">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">17.</div><div id="r17" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Memon K, Lewandowski RJ, Kulik L, Riaz A, Mulcahy MF, Salem R. Radioembolization for primary and metastatic liver cancer. <em>Semin Radiat Oncol</em> 2011;21(4):294–302.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.semradonc.2011.05.004">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21939859/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Radioembolization+for+primary+and+metastatic+liver+cancer&amp;author=K+Memon&amp;author=RJ+Lewandowski&amp;author=L+Kulik&amp;author=A+Riaz&amp;author=MF+Mulcahy&amp;author=R+Salem&amp;publication_year=2011&amp;journal=Semin+Radiat+Oncol&amp;pages=294-302&amp;doi=10.1016%2Fj.semradonc.2011.05.004&amp;pmid=21939859">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">18.</div><